      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 flex flex-col gap-1 text-[11px] text-[var(--fg-muted)]">
        <li><strong>Concrete:</strong> ACI 318 Building Code Requirements — volume formulas per ASTM C138 / C172 standards</li>
        <li><strong>Roofing:</strong> NRCA Roofing Manual — pitch multipliers per ANSI/SPRI standards; coverage data from Owens Corning, GAF, CertainTeed</li>
        <li><strong>Paint:</strong> ASTM D16 standard — coverage rates from Sherwin-Williams, Behr, PPG manufacturer specifications</li>
        <li><strong>Tile:</strong> TCNA Handbook for Ceramic, Glass, and Stone Tile Installation — waste factors per industry patterns</li>
        <li><strong>Weight calculations:</strong> Material densities per ASTM C138 (concrete), AISC Manual (steel), and published lumber species data</li>
      </ul>
